title: New Creator: Wisdom Media
body:
Name: Wisdom Media 

Socials -
https://twitter.com/WisdomMediaGG
https://wisdom-media.gg/

Info - Wisdom Media is a media company that owns and operates various gaming organizations and events in the gaming scene. With over six various organizations and event titles and their relationship with Blizzard, Wisdom Media is a premier media group in the Esports scene. Wisdom Media will be key in exploring all the opportunities that a Media company can utilize, especially in the event and Esports scene. 

Use Cases -
Coin distribution - Twitch stream , Esports event, social media 
Holding - Access to advising, social media engagement, exclusive content from events, exclusive Discord access
Transacting - Event admission, donating to event prize pool, sponsorship opportunities, consulting

Grant - $1000

A 'yes' approves Wisdom Media and a $1000 treasury grant
A 'no' denies this prop.
